FT  02 APR 93 / UK Company News: Exports rise helps lift Prestwick 31%
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Prestwick Holdings, the printed circuit board manufacturer, raised pre-tax
profits by 31 per cent, from Pounds 81,000 to Pounds 106,000, in the half
year to January 31.
The two principal plants at Irvine and Ayr increased overall sales by 20 per
