68 per cent and 89 per cent across the group. Sales came to Pounds 18.1m
(Pounds 13.9m).
Additional operating profit earned from the increased sales was adversely
affected by development costs associated with new contracts, and disruption
costs caused by erratic delivery demands from some customers.
After the preference divided there were losses per share for the period of
0.02p (0.13p). The interim dividend is held at 0.5p.
